(24, 'HTML Metin Biçimlendirme Etiketleri', '<p><img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.algoritmaornekleri.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/html-metin-bi%C3%A7imlenirme-etiketleri.png?fit=600%2C320&amp;ssl=1\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\"></p><p><br></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\">Bu yazımızda&nbsp;<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\">HTML&nbsp;</span>ile metin düzenleme etiketlerinin kullanımını göreceğiz. Metin düzenlemede kullanılan&nbsp;<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\">H1, H2, H3, H4, H5, H6, p, b, i, sup, sub,&nbsp;&nbsp;nbsp, br, hr, strong, em, blockquote, s</span>&nbsp;etiketlerinin ne işe yaradığını ve örnek kullanımını yazının devamında bulabilirsiniz.</p><div class=\"yazil-yaziici\" id=\"yazil-1506651459\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 1px auto; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; text-align: center;\"></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><span id=\"more-5047\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></p><h2 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: Roboto; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(35, 35, 35); font-size: 40px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\">Başlık Etiketi &lt;HX&gt;&nbsp;</span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\">Bu etiket hazırlamış olduğunuz dokümana başlık eklemek için kullanılmaktadır. h1, h2, h3, h4, h5 ve h6 etiketi olarak kullanılmaktadır.&nbsp;<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\">&lt;h1&gt;…&lt;/h1&gt;</span>&nbsp;en büyük başlığı&nbsp;<span style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\">&lt;h6&gt;…&lt;/h6&gt;</span>&nbsp;ise enküçük başlığı ifade etmektedir. Aşağıdaki örneği ve ekran çıktısını inceleyerek aralarındaki farkı görebilirsiniz.</p><blockquote class=\"blockquote\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: italic; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><u>Kodun Kullanımı :</u></span></p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); padding: 0px; font-size: 11px; font-family: verdana, tahoma; line-height: 22px;\"><font color=\"#ff0000\">&lt;h1&gt;</font><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">Başlık-1</span><font color=\"#ff0000\">&lt;/h1&gt;</font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); padding: 0px; font-size: 11px; font-family: verdana, tahoma; line-height: 22px;\"><font color=\"#ff0000\">&lt;h2&gt;</font><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">Başlık-2</span><font color=\"#ff0000\">&lt;/h2&gt;</font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); padding: 0px; font-size: 11px; font-family: verdana, tahoma; line-height: 22px;\"><font color=\"#ff0000\">&lt;h3&gt;</font><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">Başlık-3</span><font color=\"#ff0000\">&lt;/h3&gt;</font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); padding: 0px; font-size: 11px; font-family: verdana, tahoma; line-height: 22px;\"><font color=\"#ff0000\">&lt;h4&gt;</font><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">Başlık-4</span><font color=\"#ff0000\">&lt;/h4&gt;</font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); padding: 0px; font-size: 11px; font-family: verdana, tahoma; line-height: 22px;\"><font color=\"#ff0000\">&lt;h5&gt;</font><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">Başlık-5</span><font color=\"#ff0000\">&lt;/h5&gt;</font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(78, 78, 78); padding: 0px; font-size: 11px; font-family: verdana, tahoma; line-height: 22px;\"><font color=\"#ff0000\">&lt;h6&gt;</font><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">Başlık-6</span><font color=\"#ff0000\">&lt;/h6&gt;</font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 11px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: verdana, tahoma; line-height: 22px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 11px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: verdana, tahoma; line-height: 22px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 11px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: verdana, tahoma; line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 20px;\"><u>Ekran Çıktısı :</u></span><br></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 11px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: verdana, tahoma; line-height: 22px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 45px; outline: 0px;